, 255, 255, 0.95)\",\"textDecoration\":\"underline\",\"fontWeight\":600},\"children\":\"Browse our directory\"}],\" to find indoor dog parks near you.\"]}]]}]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-section\",\"style\":{\"padding\":\"40px 20px\"},\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-container\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-content-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-text-content\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-section-title\",\"children\":\"Meet Our Team\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-text\",\"children\":[\"The IndoorDogPark team started this project after struggling to find reliable information about indoor dog facilities. What began as a personal research project evolved into a comprehensive directory serving dog owners across the United States. We're a small team of dog lovers, researchers, and developers dedicated to making it easier for pet parents to find safe, climate-controlled play spaces for their dogs. Every listing is verified, every detail matters. Explore our \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/states\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#10b981\",\"textDecoration\":\"underline\",\"fontWeight\":600},\"children\":\"state-by-state directory\"}],\" to discover facilities in your area.\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-stats-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-stat-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"stat-number stat-green\",\"children\":\"500+\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"stat-label\",\"children\":\"Verified Listings\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-stat-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"stat-number stat-pink\",\"children\":\"150+\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"stat-label\",\"children\":\"Cities Covered\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-stat-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"stat-number stat-green\",\"children\":\"50\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"stat-label\",\"children\":\"States\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-stat-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"stat-number stat-pink\",\"children\":\"24/7\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"stat-label\",\"children\":\"Free Access\"}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-image-content\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"figure\",null,{\"style\":{\"margin\":0},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L1b\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/about/team.webp\",\"alt\":\"The IndoorDogPark.org team working together to build the best dog park directory\",\"width\":600,\"height\":500,\"style\":{\"width\":\"100%\",\"height\":\"500px\",\"borderRadius\":\"1rem\",\"objectFit\":\"cover\",\"objectPosition\":\"center\"}}],[\"$\",\"figcaption\",null,{\"style\":{\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"marginTop\":\"0.75rem\",\"fontSize\":\"0.875rem\",\"color\":\"#64748b\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\"},\"children\":\"The IndoorDogPark.org Team — Building the most comprehensive dog park directory\"}]]}]}]]}]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-section-alt\",\"style\":{\"padding\":\"40px 20px\"},\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-section-title-center\",\"children\":\"What We Do & Tips for First-Time Visitors\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-timeline\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"timeline-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"timeline-dot timeline-green\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"timeline-card\",\"children\":[\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\"]}]]}],\"$L1e\",\"$L1f\",\"$L20\",\"$L21\",\"$L22\"]}]]}]}],\"$L23\",\"$L24\",\"$L25\",\"$L26\",\"$L27\",\"$L28\",\"$L29\"]}],\"$L2a\"]}],null,\"$L2b\"]}]\n10:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[\