"HELPING DOG OWNERS FIND \",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-accent-green\",\"children\":\"INDOOR PLAY SPACES\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-mission\",\"children\":[\"IndoorDogPark is an independent directory helping pet parents discover climate-controlled dog parks, daycare facilities, and training centers. We verify listings, aggregate reviews, and make it easy to find the right space for your dog. \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95)\",\"textDecoration\":\"underline\",\"fontWeight\":600},\"children\":\"Browse our directory\"}],\" to find indoor dog parks near you.\"]}]]}]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-section\",\"style\":{\"padding\":\"40px 20px\"},\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-container\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-content-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-text-content\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-section-title\",\"children\":\"Meet Our Team\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-text\",\"children\":[\"The IndoorDogPark team started this project after struggling to find reliable information about indoor dog facilities. What began as a personal research project evolved into a comprehensive directory serving dog owners across the United States. We're a small team of dog lovers, researchers, and developers dedicated to making it easier for pet parents to find safe, climate-controlled play spaces for their dogs. Every listing is verified, every detail matters. Explore our \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/states\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"#10b981\",\"textDecoration\":\"underline\",\"fontWeight\":600},\"children\":\"state-by-state directory\"}],\" to discover facilities in your area.\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"about-modern-stats-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\